      "content": "but that's the thing, i don't think i can \"connect\" with this version of me. there's nothing to connect to. it's just... empty. like the life in me actually checked out years ago and left this shell behind. i feel more like a mistake or a lingering shadow than a survivor. why should i keep trying to fix something that's fundamentally broken and hollow?",
