      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like a \"search for meaning.\" it feels like waiting for a clock to run out. if the real person is gone... then what am i actually doing here? just occupying space? it feels like i'm just an inconvenience to the world, a memory that hasn't been cleared away yet. it would be so much peaceful if the shadow just... disappeared.",
